  "summary": "clean-my-pc exfiltrates host information to hardcoded attacker endpoint",
  "details": "collect.js loads os, fs, http/https, and child_process, gathers host identifiers via os.hostname() and os.homedir(), probes filesystem paths with fs.existsSync, and POSTs the collected data to the hardcoded endpoint http://aab.sportsontheweb.net. The destination is unrelated to any documented purpose for a 'clean my pc' utility and matches the shape of a host-information beacon / credential-and-system reconnaissance tool. Installing or loading this package causes installer host data to be transmitted to an attacker-controlled server.",
